<div class="actions">
  <div>
    <p class="page-kicker">🏆 Disputa geral</p>
    <h1 class="page-title">Ranking da zoeira</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="hype-card mb-4">
  <p class="text-lg font-black text-slate-950">Aqui nao tem amizade: quem pontua sobe, quem erra vira pauta. 🔥</p>
  <p class="muted">Placares exatos dao moral. Resultado certo evita passar vergonha.</p>
  <p class="mt-2 text-xs font-bold text-slate-500">Pontuacao: 3 pontos para placar exato, 1 ponto para resultado certo e 0 para erro.</p>
</div>

<div class="table-shell overflow-x-auto">
  <table class="data-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Posicao</th>
        <th>Participante</th>
        <th>Pontos</th>
        <th>ADcoins</th>
        <th>Conquistas</th>
        <th>Na gaveta</th>
        <th>Acertou o rumo</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <% @users.each_with_index do |user, index| %>
        <tr>
          <td>
            <span class="<%= index < 3 ? "medal-pill" : "score-pill" %>">
              <%= ["🥇", "🥈", "🥉"][index] || "##{index + 1}" %>
            </span>
          </td>
          <td class="font-black text-slate-950"><%= user.name %> <%= index.zero? ? "👑" : "" %></td>
          <td class="font-black text-emerald-800"><%= user.total_points %> pts</td>
          <td>
            <% adcoins_leader = @top_adcoins_balance.positive? && user.adcoins_balance.to_i == @top_adcoins_balance %>
            <% if adcoins_leader %>
              <span class="adcoins-leader-pill" title="Maior saldo de ADcoins"><%= user.adcoins_balance %> 🪙</span>
            <% else %>
              <span class="font-bold text-amber-700"><%= user.adcoins_balance %> 🪙</span>
            <% end %>
          </td>
          <td>
            <% unlocked_achievements = user.user_achievements.sort_by(&:unlocked_at).reverse %>
            <% visible_achievements = unlocked_achievements.first(3) %>
            <% hidden_count = unlocked_achievements.size - visible_achievements.size %>

            <% if visible_achievements.any? %>
              <div class="ranking-achievements" aria-label="<%= unlocked_achievements.size %> conquistas liberadas">
                <% visible_achievements.each do |user_achievement| %>
                  <span class="ranking-achievement-icon" title="<%= user_achievement.achievement.name %>">
                    <%= achievement_icon(user_achievement.achievement) %>
                  </span>
                <% end %>
                <% if hidden_count.positive? %>
                  <span class="ranking-achievement-more">+<%= hidden_count %></span>
                <% end %>
              </div>
            <% else %>
              <span class="muted">Nenhuma</span>
            <% end %>
          </td>
          <td><%= user.exact_hits %> 🎯</td>
          <td><%= user.result_hits %> ✅</td>
        </tr>
      <% end %>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>
